{
  "screen_id": "settings",
  "route": "/s/settings",
  "title": "設定",
  "layout": "standard",
  "notes": "選好(locale/theme_pack_id/reduced_motion_override)を PATCH /api/v1/me/preferences で追記(append-only・LWW 投影)。現在値は GET /api/v1/me/preferences。V3-I18-08/UIX-16。V3-UIX-43: /me/settings 集約ハブとして、既に別 screen-def で自己完結する設定機能(AI接続BYOK・機器連携SwitchBot・テーマfork)への導線+この画面自身が持つ選好(表示言語/テーマ/モーション/UI露出/Push通知)+自己データ持出し(バックアップ代替のCSVエクスポート)を1画面に集約する。Push通知は選好の保持のみで実配信基盤(VAPID鍵)は人間ゲート(§5・実鍵投入)。アカウント統合(複数アカウントのマージ)はTruth append-onlyモデルとの整合設計が未確定のため対象外(裁定待ち・要検討: 統合時に元actor_idの履歴をどう畳み込むか)。",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "shell",
      "type": "app-shell",
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "page",
          "type": "page",
          "children": [
            { "id": "title", "type": "heading", "props": { "text_key": "settings.title.text", "text": "設定", "level": 1 } },
            {
              "id": "current",
              "type": "card",
              "props": { "source_path": "/api/v1/me/preferences" },
              "children": [
                { "id": "current-title", "type": "heading", "props": { "text_key": "settings.current-title.text", "text": "現在の設定", "level": 2 } },
                { "id": "current-locale", "type": "text", "props": { "text_key": "settings.current-locale.text", "text": "言語: {{data.current.locale}}" } },
                { "id": "current-theme", "type": "text", "props": { "text_key": "settings.current-theme.text", "text": "テーマ: {{data.current.theme_pack_id}}", "muted": true } },
                { "id": "current-motion", "type": "text", "props": { "text_key": "settings.current-motion.text", "text": "モーション設定: {{data.current.reduced_motion_override}}", "muted": true } },
                { "id": "current-exposure", "type": "text", "props": { "text_key": "settings.current-exposure.text", "text": "UI露出: {{data.current.ui_exposure}}", "muted": true } },
                { "id": "current-push", "type": "text", "props": { "text_key": "settings.current-push.text", "text": "Push通知: {{data.current.push_notifications_enabled}}", "muted": true } },
                { "id": "current-delivery", "type": "text", "props": { "text_key": "settings.current-delivery.text", "text": "受取方法: {{data.current.delivery_pref}}", "muted": true } },
                { "id": "current-bank", "type": "text", "props": { "text_key": "settings.current-bank.text", "text": "銀行振込の受け取り準備: {{data.current.bank_transfer_ready}}", "muted": true } }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "pref-form",
              "type": "form",
              "action": { "kind": "api", "method": "PATCH", "path": "/api/v1/me/preferences", "body_from": "pref-form" },
              "children": [
                { "id": "locale", "type": "field", "props": { "variant": "select", "name": "locale", "label_key": "settings.locale.label", "label": "言語", "placeholder": "言語を選ぶ", "options": [
                  { "value": "ja", "label": "日本語" },
                  { "value": "en", "label": "English" }
                ] } },
                { "id": "theme", "type": "field", "props": { "variant": "select", "name": "theme_pack_id", "label_key": "settings.theme.label", "label": "テーマ", "placeholder": "テーマを選ぶ", "options": [
                  { "value": "minimal-light", "label": "ライト" },
                  { "value": "minimal-dark", "label": "ダーク" }
                ] } },
                { "id": "motion", "type": "field", "props": { "variant": "select", "name": "reduced_motion_override", "label_key": "settings.motion.label", "label": "モーションを減らす", "placeholder": "モーション設定を選ぶ", "options": [
                  { "value": "system", "label": "端末の設定に従う" },
                  { "value": "reduce", "label": "減らす" },
                  { "value": "no-preference", "label": "制限しない" }
                ] } },
                { "id": "ui-exposure", "type": "field", "props": { "variant": "select", "name": "ui_exposure", "label_key": "settings.ui-exposure.label", "label": "UI露出(開発者向け表示)", "placeholder": "UI露出を選ぶ", "options": [
                  { "value": "user", "label": "一般(既定)" },
                  { "value": "dev", "label": "開発者向け表示も見る" },
                  { "value": "admin", "label": "管理者向け表示も見る" }
                ] } },
                { "id": "push-enabled", "type": "field", "props": { "variant": "select", "name": "push_notifications_enabled", "label_key": "settings.push-enabled.label", "label": "Push通知", "placeholder": "Push通知を選ぶ", "options": [
                  { "value": "off", "label": "オフ(既定)" },
                  { "value": "on", "label": "オン" }
                ] } },
                { "id": "delivery-pref", "type": "field", "props": { "variant": "select", "name": "delivery_pref", "label_key": "settings.delivery-pref.label", "label": "受取方法(取引前準備・V3-UIX-80)", "placeholder": "受取方法を選ぶ", "options": [
                  { "value": "post_office_hold", "label": "郵便局留め・はこぽす(匿名受取)" },
                  { "value": "home_delivery", "label": "自宅配送(相手と直接URLをやり取り)" }
                ] } },
                { "id": "bank-transfer-ready", "type": "field", "props": { "variant": "select", "name": "bank_transfer_ready", "label_key": "settings.bank-transfer-ready.label", "label": "銀行振込の受け取り準備(取引前準備・V3-UIX-80)", "placeholder": "選ぶ", "options": [
                  { "value": "no", "label": "まだ(既定)" },
                  { "value": "yes", "label": "準備できている" }
                ] } },
                { "id": "save", "type": "button", "props": { "label_key": "settings.save.label", "label": "設定を保存する", "variant": "primary", "type": "submit" } }
              ]
            },
            { "id": "hub-title", "type": "heading", "props": { "text_key": "settings.hub-title.text", "text": "その他の設定", "level": 2 } },
            { "id": "hub-ai", "type": "link", "props": { "label_key": "settings.hub-ai.label", "label": "AI接続設定(BYOK・個体観測用LLM等)", "href": "/s/ai-profile-settings" } },
            { "id": "hub-device", "type": "link", "props": { "label_key": "settings.hub-device.label", "label": "機器連携(SwitchBot等IoT)", "href": "/devices" } },
            { "id": "hub-theme", "type": "link", "props": { "label_key": "settings.hub-theme.label", "label": "テーマのfork一覧", "href": "/s/theme-gallery" } },
            { "id": "backup-title", "type": "heading", "props": { "text_key": "settings.backup-title.text", "text": "自分のデータを持ち出す(バックアップ)", "level": 2 } },
            { "id": "backup-facts", "type": "link", "props": { "label_key": "settings.backup-facts.label", "label": "個体データをCSVで書き出す", "href": "/api/v1/export/facts.csv" } },
            { "id": "backup-photos", "type": "link", "props": { "label_key": "settings.backup-photos.label", "label": "写真参照一覧をCSVで書き出す", "href": "/api/v1/export/photos.csv" } },
            {
              "id": "next-step",
              "type": "link",
              "props": { "label_key": "settings.next.label", "label": "ホームに戻る", "href": "/", "next_step": "ホームに戻る" }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "transitions": [
    { "from": "pref-form", "to_screen_id": "settings", "label": "保存後に再読込(I18-03: 新localeでUI全文を即時切替)" }
  ]
}
